snippet.title: Kinect for Xbox 360 - Kinect(TM) Joy Ride
snippet.description:
You'll need more than your thumbs if you want to win at Kinect Joy Ride! Enjoy classic karting action full of spectacular tricks, unpredictable power-ups, and exotic locations -- all with revolutionary Kinect controls. Coming November 2010.

Find out more at: http://bit.ly/cK3Z9G


ESRB Rating: RATING PENDING
